dc_title_s: Fremont County, Iowa, 1960, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Image is a photoreduction of the mosaic created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol BKA. Form of individual image numbering: BKA-1AA-[number], or BKA-2AA-[number]."Flying completed 6-2-60""Approximate scale, 1:20,000" [refers to individual images from which mosaic was made].
